name: National Enterprises
overview: Established in the year 1991, we, “National Enterprises”, have been in the industry for the past 22 years. Being one of the leading scrap merchant, we are involved in the trading and supplying of a wide variety of products like Renewed MS Iron Barrel, Recycled Plastic Barrel & Scraps. We are also offering Reconditioning Services. We have a a huge vendor base who manufacture these products from best quality raw material along with cutting-edge technology. Keeping in mind the needs and specifications of our huge clientèle, we also offer a wide range of these products in various customized forms. We are widely appreciated by our clients for the prompt deliveries and accuracy of our products and services. We effectively deal in waste management and recycling of various scrap material. This helps our clients to reduce the consumption of fresh raw materials and prevent excess consumption of power and energy.
